OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,FA democracy pressure group in the UK,
OL,7,Fled by a former Liberal Democrat MP,
OL,8,Fsays the political movement Value
OL,9,FJersey should be more transparent with
OL,10,Fthe public over its funding model
OL,11,Fahead of the island's election.
OL,13,FThe movement, which was set up last
OL,14,Fyear, does not need to abide by
OL,15,Fexpenditure limits for the forthcoming
OL,16,Felection as they are not a political
OL,17,Fparty or a third party group.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
