PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,FHowever, ITV News understands the
OL,7,Fgroup are paying political consultancy
OL,8,Ffirms whose advice is being used to
OL,9,Fhelp candidates who choose to endorse
OL,10,Fthe group's policies in June's poll.
OL,12,FUK pressure group Unlock Democracy are
OL,13,Fconcerned that the public aren't fully
OL,14,Faware of the names of Value Jersey's
OL,15,Fdonors and their full funding model.
OL,17,FValue Jersey was set up as a political
OL,18,Fmovement with slogan to "make Jersey
OL,19,Fmore affordable" last year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,FAround nine candidates are endorsing
OL,7,Ftheir 'Purple Book' which is a set of
OL,8,Fpolicies and objectives the group want
OL,9,Fto achieve.
OL,11,FThe group say they have had 58 donors
OL,12,Fsince their launch, with the largest
OL,13,Fdonation being #10,000. It's board
OL,14,Fclaim it would be breaking data
OL,15,Fprotection laws if they revealed their
OL,16,Fnames.
OL,18,FOn 22nd April, the group sent an email
OL,19,Fto all candidates offering a "support
OL,20,Fpackage" if candidates choose to
OL,21,Fendorse the Purple Book.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,FThe email says this support includes:
OL,7,Fcampaign planning, writing speeches
OL,8,Fand emails and printed materials. If
OL,9,Fthe candidates choose to buy this
OL,10,Fsupport package, it will show up on
OL,11,Ftheir individual expense forms.
OL,13,FHowever, the group have spent money on
OL,14,Fconsultants such as the Messina Group,
OL,15,Fwhich worked on President Obama's
OL,16,Felection campaign in 2012 and the
OL,17,FConservative Party's UK General
OL,18,FElection campaign in 2015.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News, Dr
OL,7,FGraham Root, a board member for Value
OL,8,FJersey said: "We have put together a
OL,9,Fcoherent set of policies which we are
OL,10,Fhoping people who are elected will
OL,11,Fadopt and post-election, we will
OL,12,Fmonitor that"
OL,14,F"Value Jersey has used a number
OL,15,Fsuppliers since it was established. We
OL,16,Fhave a commercial contract with
OL,17,FMessina and it would be completely
OL,18,Finappropriate to reveal the contents
OL,19,Fof a commercial contract"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,F"We have said to candidates if they
OL,7,Fwish to access a level of support they
OL,8,Fare free to do so.
OL,10,F"There is no nefarious plot here. All
OL,11,Fwe want is to is to make the island a
OL,12,Fbetter place to live."
OL,14,FValue Jersey's board would not tell
OL,15,FITV how much they were charging
OL,16,Fcandidates for their support, but it
OL,17,Fwill show up on expenses after the
OL,18,Felection.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,FTom Brake, the CEO of Unlock
OL,7,FDemocracy, is concerned the public
OL,8,Faren't fully aware of the names of
OL,9,Ftheir donors and their full funding
OL,10,Fmodel.
OL,12,FHe said: "The group are trying to
OL,13,Finfluence the political process."
OL,15,F"That's why whether they are covered
OL,16,Fby the third party group expenditure
OL,17,Frules or the political party rules in
OL,18,FJersey, they need to be transparent"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
