PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,F"They need to move quite quickly on
OL,7,Fthis to ensure transparency is
OL,8,Fprovided so everyone understands who
OL,9,Fis behind them."
OL,11,FThe Jersey Electoral Authority say
OL,12,Fthey will "be making recommendations
OL,13,Fto the Privileges and Procedure
OL,14,FCommittee to amend several aspects the
OL,15,FLaw relating to expenditure going
OL,16,Fforward."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
