CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780225373
OL,3,CValue Jersey 'need to be transparent'
OL,4,Cwarns former Liberal Democrat MP
OL,6,FFurthermore, they add that any
OL,7,Fcandidate who is found to have
OL,8,Fbreached the expenditure laws will be
OL,9,Ffined and disqualified from holding
OL,10,Fthe office in which they have been
OL,11,Felected into.
OL,13,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,14,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,15,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,16,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,17,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,18,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,19,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,20,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,21,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
